### OCR image upload (requires OCR_ENABLED=true)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----ocr

------ocr
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="ocr-sample.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./ocr-sample.png
------ocr--

### OCR RAG chat
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "退款政策是什么？",
  "topK": 5
}
